snippet.textDisplay: Thanks for this amazing song. Kashmir has got immense talent and rich literature and as a Kashmiri I'm proud. Hope to see more of these collaborations. I would love to see the  likes of Mahjoor, Mehmood Gami, Rasool Mir, Haba Khatoon relived again and reach the world audience through Coke Studio. It will encourage our new generation to further enrich our culture and tradition. Hope this will not be the only collaboration of Coke Studio with Kashmir.
